<%= content_for :title, "I will refund your Lemon Squeezy renewal" %>
<%= content_for :preheader, "I will cancel and fully refund your recent LS renewal." %>
<tr>
  <td class="sm-px-0" style="width: 100%; padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; text-align: left">
    <table style="width: 100%;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <table style="width: 100%;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
              <td style="border-radius: 4px; background-color: #fff; padding: 24px; box-shadow: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)">
                <h1 style="margin: 0 0 36px; font-size: 36px; line-height: 36px; color: #000">
                  Quick update about your Premium subscription
                </h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  Hi,
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  First of all, thank you for your continued support and trust in Visualizer.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  In case you missed it, I switched my payment provider away from Lemon Squeezy.
                  As you might know from first-hand experience, LS has been pretty frustrating to work with (random network issues, odd billing behavior, no support,…).
