                  What that means is that if you were paying extra VAT/sales tax on top before, that will no longer be the case and the price will simply be 50€/year.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  If you want more context, I wrote about it in two updates:
                  <a class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline" href="https://visualizer.coffee/updates/new-year-new-payment-processor-meticulous-support-and-much-more">switching payment providers</a>
                  and
                  <a class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline" href="https://visualizer.coffee/updates/better-charts-clearer-bags-and-trending-tweaks">payment providers update</a>.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  Unfortunately, there is no automatic migration path, but because your yearly plan renewed after New Year, I will shortly cancel that subscription and <strong>issue a full refund</strong>.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  After that, you are free to sign up again at
                  <a class="hover-no-underline" target="_blank" style="color: #db3e27; text-decoration-line: underline" href="https://visualizer.coffee/premium">visualizer.coffee/premium</a>.
                  It will go through Creem automatically.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  If your country adds sales tax (VAT or similar), this will likely be cheaper for you.
                  And even in the worst case, the price stays the same - just on a better and more reliable platform.
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  Thank you for your understanding and for continuing support Visualizer. It really means a lot!
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; color: #000">
                  Miha
                </p>
